Why are you beating yourself up over this one?

422
00:18:18,458 --> 00:18:20,224
你知道原因的 Dwayne
You know why, Dwayne.

423
00:18:20,226 --> 00:18:21,859
你看到了庭审录像
You saw the courtroom footage.

424
00:18:21,861 --> 00:18:23,594
那不是我原本的样子
I wasn't myself.

425
00:18:24,864 --> 00:18:27,598
