I take it you knew Janet Ortega, too?

431
00:18:49,222 --> 00:18:51,923
当然 她早上坐Jack开的电车上班
Well, sure. She rode Jack's streetcar to work

432
00:18:51,925 --> 00:18:54,325
晚上坐我开的电车回家
on the early shift, mine back home at night.

433
00:18:54,327 --> 00:18:56,127
基本上每天都能见到她
Saw her pretty much every day.

434
00:18:56,129 --> 00:18:57,595
她和Jack在一起的时候挺好的
She and Jack were good together.

435
00:18:57,597 --> 00:18:59,096
知道他害死了她
Until he killed her.

436
00:18:59,098 --> 00:19:00,998
