Still can't believe he did it.

437
00:19:01,000 --> 00:19:02,867
意思是 你觉得他是无辜的
Meaning, what? You think he was innocent?

438
00:19:02,869 --> 00:19:05,469
那时候是的 我是说 我知道他有多爱她
At the time, yeah. I mean, I know how much he loved her.

439
00:19:05,471 --> 00:19:08,139
Jack一生都忍受着
Jack struggled with paranoia and delusions

440
00:19:08,141 --> 00:19:09,340
偏执与幻觉的折磨
his whole life.

441
00:19:09,342 --> 00:19:11,709
我以为他的情况已经得到控制
I thought he had it under control.

442
00:19:11,711 --> 00:19:13,711
当时地方检察官引导你在法庭上这么说的
Is that what the D.A. got you to say in court?

443
00:19:13,713 --> 00:19:15,880
是的 这成了他定罪的依据
Yeah. It helped send him away.

444
00:19:15,882 --> 00:19:18,349
好吧 他现在出狱了 若他为了报仇
Yeah, well, he's out now, and if he killed Karen Decker

445
00:19:18,351 --> 00:19:20,585
杀了Karen Decker 那你也不安全
out of revenge, then you're not safe, either.

446
00:19:20,587 --> 00:19:22,053
你能否帮我们想想
Is there any chance you might help us figure out

447
00:19:22,055 --> 00:19:23,955
在哪儿能找到Gordon
where Gordon might be?

448
00:19:23,957 --> 00:19:25,790
我是说 我们越快抓到他
I mean, the sooner we get him off the streets,

449
00:19:25,792 --> 00:19:28,860
就能越早保障其他指正过他的人的人身安全
the sooner the people who testified against him are safe.

450
00:19:28,862 --> 00:19:30,728
我觉得今天早些时候我看到Jack了
I think I saw Jack earlier today,

451
00:19:30,730 --> 00:19:32,263
在车站对面的马路上
across the street from the station.

452
00:19:32,265 --> 00:19:33,998
你当时为什么不报警
So, why didn't you call the police?

453
00:19:34,000 --> 00:19:35,900
我当时不确定那是他
I wasn't sure it was him.

454
00:19:35,902 --> 00:19:38,302
况且 我当时也不知道他又杀人了
Besides, I didn't know he'd just killed somebody else.

455
00:19:47,480 --> 00:19:49,680
-好消息 -嗯
- Uh, good news. - Mm-hmm.

456
00:19:49,682 --> 00:19:52,149
Christopher说所有指证过Gordon的人
Christopher says everyone who testified against Gordon,

457
00:19:52,151 --> 00:19:54,118
都被警方保护了
under police protection.

458
00:19:54,120 --> 00:19:55,586
很显然 我也是 拿着
Apparently, so am I. Here.

459
00:19:56,756 --> 00:19:58,256
噢 对了 我睡觉不打呼
Oh, by the way. I don't snore.

460
00:19:58,258 --> 00:20:00,992
至少就我所知 不打呼
At least, not that I know of, anymore.

461
00:20:02,128 --> 00:20:04,061
我不知道我还打不打呼
I don't know if I do anymore.

462
00:20:04,063 --> 00:20:06,430
你觉得我们其中的一个还会再婚吗
You think either of us will ever get married again?

463
00:20:06,432 --> 00:20:09,066
噢 我自己倒是不着急 你呢
Oh, I'm not in any hurry, myself. You?

464
00:20:09,068 --> 00:20:11,969
如果遇到对的人 也许会吧
If the right person came along, maybe.

465
00:20:11,971 --> 00:20:14,872
前一段婚姻让我挺失望的
Last one kind of soured me on the idea.

466
00:20:14,874 --> 00:20:17,074
是啊 不过也是很久以前的事了
Yeah. Long time ago, though.

467
00:20:18,144 --> 00:20:22,046
就在Gordon的案子之前离的婚 对吗
Divorce happened just before Gordon's case, didn't it?

468
00:20:22,048 --> 00:20:24,081
那是我搬到了这里的原因
That's the reason I moved here.

469
00:20:24,083 --> 00:20:26,284
一个崭新的开始
New beginnings and all.

470
00:20:26,286 --> 00:20:28,252
是啊 有许多要经历的
