471
00:20:29,989 --> 00:20:33,925
Gordon的案子肯定让一切变得更加困难了
Gordon's case must've made it even harder.

472
00:20:33,927 --> 00:20:36,127
我们这是要聊什么 Dwayne
Where are we going with all this, Dwayne?

