475
00:20:42,135 --> 00:20:44,335
不 不是他对我不好
No, it isn't that he didn't treat me right.

476
00:20:44,337 --> 00:20:47,872
你知道的 他疏远我了
You know it. He froze me out.

477
00:20:47,874 --> 00:20:49,607
一开始他不是这样的
He wasn't like this at first,

478
00:20:49,609 --> 00:20:53,778
自从他开始嫉妒我的成功
just started to resent my success.

479
00:20:53,780 --> 00:20:55,313
事情变得越来越糟
Then it got even worse

480
00:20:55,315 --> 00:20:59,383
当他被还不如他够格的人淘汰后
when they passed him over for others less qualified.

481
00:20:59,385 --> 00:21:01,285
