00:21:48,067 --> 00:21:51,102
我当时并不是想让Gordon付出代价
I wasn't trying to make Gordon pay.

501
00:21:51,104 --> 00:21:53,904
我是想让我的丈夫付出代价
I was trying to make my husband pay.

502
00:21:55,575 --> 00:21:58,476
从此以后这事就挥之不去
And it's haunted me ever since.

