这是一份好工作
It's a great job.

901
00:39:29,827 --> 00:39:32,228
爱工作的每一分钟
Loved every minute of it.

902
00:39:34,966 --> 00:39:37,066
也许我可以帮点儿忙
Might be able to pull some strings,

903
00:39:37,068 --> 00:39:40,436
看看我能否让你重拾工作
see if I can get you your-your job back.

904
00:39:40,438 --> 00:39:43,105
你现在是自由的 Jack 除此之外 这个城市和政府
You're a free man now, Jack. Besides, the city and the state,

905
00:39:43,107 --> 00:39:46,809
-欠你的不止这些 -可是
- they owe you more than that. - Still,

906
00:39:46,811 --> 00:39:49,779
突然出狱并洗脱了罪名还是让我
it's a little scary being out all of a sudden,

907
00:39:49,781 --> 00:39:51,547
有点害怕
cleared.

908
00:39:51,549 --> 00:39:54,116
我花了这么多年尝试证明我的清白
I spent so many years trying to prove my innocence,

909
00:39:54,118 --> 00:39:56,919
我都没怎么想 如果我成功了该去做什么
I didn't think much about what I'd do if I succeeded.

910
00:39:56,921 --> 00:40:01,157
教习所可以帮你去适应
Well, the-the halfway house can help you adjust.

911
00:40:01,159 --> 00:40:02,625
我也可以
So can I.

912
00:40:02,627 --> 00:40:04,527
Wade医生也可以
So can Dr. Wade.

913
00:40:04,529 --> 00:40:08,297
这就是你来见我 和我一起坐车的原因么
Is that why you wanted to meet, ride with me?

914
00:40:08,299 --> 00:40:11,534
只是其中一个原因
One of the reasons.

915
00:40:11,536 --> 00:40:13,169
听着
Look...

916
00:40:15,473 --> 00:40:18,140
你向她寻求帮助
...you were right to...

917
00:40:18,142 --> 00:40:21,277
是正确的
go to her for help.

918
00:40:21,279 --> 00:40:24,847
现在也没有理由停止 Jack
There's no reason to stop now, Jack.

919
00:40:25,817 --> 00:40:27,917
她为发生的事感到很难过
She feels bad about what happened,

920
00:40:27,919 --> 00:40:29,618
比她应得的还难过
more than she deserves.

921
00:40:29,620 --> 00:40:33,489
难过 天 她不是才帮我洗脱罪名了么
Bad? Hell, didn't she just help exonerate me?

922
00:40:34,759 --> 00:40:37,693
而且 我从来没有怪过她
Anyway, I never held anything against her.

923
00:40:37,695 --> 00:40:39,328
我的意思是 她什么都没有做错
I mean, she didn't do anything wrong.

924
00:40:39,330 --> 00:40:41,397
我 我伤害了Janet
I... I hurt Janet.

925
00:40:41,399 --> 00:40:43,699
而这事儿被用来反击我
Got used against me.

926
00:40:43,701 --> 00:40:46,035
所有她做的只是说了出来
All she did was say it.

927
00:40:46,037 --> 00:40:47,636
事实上
Actually,

928
00:40:47,638 --> 00:40:49,939
或许是她最后救了我的命
she probably ended up saving my life,

929
00:40:49,941 --> 00:40:52,975
因为我的情况让陪审团同情我
getting the jury to take pity on me 'cause of my condition.

930
00:40:52,977 --> 00:40:54,677
那么你也有可能接受我来找你谈话的
Then maybe you'll be open to the other reason

931
00:40:54,679 --> 00:40:55,945
另一个原因
I wanted to talk to you.

932
00:40:55,947 --> 00:40:58,347
这个优秀的医生在无辜者计划中
The good doctor's donated her time

933
00:40:58,349 --> 00:41:01,016
贡献了她多年的时间
to the Innocence Project for a lot of years.

934
00:41:01,018 --> 00:41:04,987
你能否用你所了解的 去帮助其他遭受错误监禁的人
Could you use what you learned to help others wrongly imprisoned.

935
00:41:04,989 --> 00:41:08,124
这也许会给你一些方向
Might give you some direction.

936
00:41:08,126 --> 00:41:12,561
也许 能帮助你们两个有所恢复
Maybe... help the two of you heal a little bit.

937
00:41:14,265 --> 00:41:16,298
有兴趣吗
Interested?

938
00:41:26,377 --> 00:41:28,911
收藏么
Storage?

939
00:41:28,913 --> 00:41:31,113
不 垃圾
No. Trash.

940
00:41:31,115 --> 00:41:33,916
我不会再背负沉重的过去
I'm not gonna let the past weigh me down any longer.

941
00:41:33,918 --> 00:41:36,051
是时候前进了
It's time to move on.

942
00:41:36,053 --> 00:41:39,655
除非你想让我多聊聊我的前夫来烦你
Unless you want me to bore you with more talk of my ex-husband.

943
00:41:39,657 --> 00:41:40,890
我要出去了
I'm out of here.

944
00:41:40,892 --> 00:41:43,125
那正是我想要的
Mm, that's what I thought.

945
00:42:08,486 --> 00:42:10,686
谢谢
Thank you.

946
00:42:15,247 --> 00:42:18,794
你想进来喝杯茶么 Gordon先生
Would you like to come in for some tea, Mr. Gordon?

947
00:42:20,915 --> 00:42:23,115
当然
Sure.

